sql:
SELECT ts.team_id
FROM team_seasons ts
WHERE ts.season_id = (SELECT MAX(season_id) FROM seasons);

SELECT DISTINCT pp.player_name
FROM player_performance pp
WHERE pp.goals_scored > 5;

external_knowledge:
Soccer is a sport; 
A team's identity can be represented by its unique identifier and name; 
A summary of a team's performance can be understood through its total wins, losses, draws, and average score.
